com.stripe.android

Class EphemeralKey

  • com.stripe.android.EphemeralKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StripeModel

    public class EphemeralKey
implements StripeModel

    Represents an Ephemeral Key that can be used temporarily for API operations that typically require a secret key.

    See https://stripe.com/docs/mobile/android/standard#prepare-your-api for more details on ephemeral keys.

    See Also:
    https://stripe.com/docs/mobile/android/standard#prepare-your-api
